{"type": "article", "id": 2581, "title": "Normann Copenhagen  Geo 系列新品", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-26T08:13:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232248NbU83QPClSqYi0cf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 日前为其曾获奖的 Geo 系列再添 6 款新品，出自丹麦设计师 Nicholai Wiig Hansen 之手，其极致简约的整体造型搭配着锋利的边缘设计，舍弃了不必要的细节显出独特的几何美感。Geo 全新系列包括一个真空保温杯、一个托盘、一个糖罐以及三款不同大小的带盖罐子。定价 15-90 美元不等，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/families/geo-collection\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232246okw3gzcsjq8lxIn1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052322479TC0o4Yz1XsJ3Lam.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052322476G4SYTyAmVWiOBxe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232247QNmsRoK47EOTag6r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}